:::Child did as he is bidden, he goes to his room and packs his things. He 
find something he dident think is father had let him pack, it was his 
computer. he stows it In a secret pouch then he took it out and turned it on. 
He taped keys and finally got the program he wanted

Child: "Computer print out the history of earth in digital form."

The computer began to download information on earth into his head. he sorted 
it all out and then found what he was looking for. the mountain that they 
were moving to. The found the chambers and then he found it. a secluded 
chambered with a small entrance at the top of the mountain. he would use that 
to practice his powers and to get away from the hustle and bustle of life. He 
put that in his long term memo bank and continued packing:::
